videos.description: The Nets fans in attendance greet Blake Griffin with an ovation as he checks into the game for the first time.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Griffin checks in to an ovation) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin checks in to an ovation

videos.description: Bradley Beal tries to go baseline for a layup, but Blake Griffin jumps high to swat the shot away.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Griffin rises up to deny Beal) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin rises up to deny Beal

videos.description: James Harden shows off some handles before drilling a 3-pointer from the wing.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden cooks up 3-pointer from the wing) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden cooks up 3-pointer from the wing

videos.description: Garrison Mathews' shoulder accidentally collides with James Harden's head. Harden would remain down for a few moments.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden shaken up after collision with Mathews) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden shaken up after collision with Mathews

videos.description: Joe Harris passes to a driving DeAndre Jordan, who throws down a dunk while drawing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harris dishes to Jordan for and-1 dunk) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris dishes to Jordan for and-1 dunk

videos.description: James Harden's pass to DeAndre Jordan is a little off, but before he falls out of bounds, Jordan manages to smack it back to Harden for a layup

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan finds Harden falling out of bounds) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan finds Harden falling out of bounds

videos.description: During the third quarter, James Harden and Russell Westbrook share a brief moment with a short handshake.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden, Westbrook exchange a brief handshake) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden, Westbrook exchange a brief handshake

videos.description: Blake Griffin drives in and flushes it down for his first points as a Net and his first dunk since 2019.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Griffin's first points as a Net end his dunking drought) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin's first points as a Net end his dunking drought
